nd of herbage, (Msb,) and of palm-trees: (Msb, TA:) [app. used as epithets and as substs.: see also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EavariY~N","text_ar":"عَثَرِىٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":": and see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baEolN","text_ar":"بَعْلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":":] and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ea*K","text_ar":"عَذٍ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ea*iY~N","text_ar":"عَذِىٌّ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", the latter of the measure"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"faEiylN","text_ar":"فَعِيلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", are applied as epithets to the same in the same sense: the pl. of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"E*oYN","text_ar":"عذْىٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aEo*aA='N","text_ar":"اَعْذَا=ءٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Msb.) ―         -b2-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ei*oYu AlkalaA^i","text_ar":"عِذْىُ الكَلَاِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Herbage,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pasturage, that is remote from the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"riyf","text_ar":"رِيف"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"land of sown fields and of seed produce"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.],"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and that grows from the rain."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b3-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ei*oYN","text_ar":"عِذْىٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A place that gives growth to plants,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"herbage, in winter and summer, without the welling forth of water."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Lth, TA.) ―         -b4-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Any place not having in it"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"plants of the kind called"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HamoD","text_ar":"حَمْض"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"nor land that exudes water and produces salt;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ea*oYN","text_ar":"عَذْىٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K.) ―         -b5-  And"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"i. q."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ea*aApN","text_ar":"عَذَاةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": [perhaps in the sense last expl. above: (see the latter in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"E*w","text_ar":"عذو"},{"kind":"text","text":":)] pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aEo*aA='N","text_ar":"اَعْذَا=ءٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (TA.)"}],"source_refs":["S","Msb","K","IAar","TA"]},{"entry_id":"n28506","headword_ar":"عَذِىٌّ","root":"E*Y","body":[{"kind":"text","text":": see the next preceding paragraph."}],"source_refs":[]}]},"classical_definitions":null}